sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Dev as 维护者(小龙)
    participant Plan as ModuleRenamePlan
    participant Edit as 批量编辑脚本
    participant FS as 文件系统
    participant Go as Go 工具链
    participant FE as 前端测试
    participant CI as GitHub Actions

    Note over Dev,CI: 阶段 1 — module 声明 + Go 源码批量改写
    Dev->>Plan: 加载 rename 配置<br/>(old=pantheon-platform, new=pantheon-base)
    Plan->>Edit: 生成 FileEdit 列表
    Edit->>FS: 修改 backend/go.mod module 声明
    Edit->>FS: 批量替换 142 个 .go 文件 import<br/>"pantheon-platform/" → "pantheon-base/"
    Edit->>Go: gofmt -w backend/
    Go-->>Edit: 格式 OK
    Edit->>Go: go mod tidy
    Go-->>Edit: 依赖一致
    Edit->>Go: go build ./... && go vet ./...
    Go-->>Dev: 编译通过

    Note over Dev,CI: 阶段 2 — 代码生成器模板
    Dev->>FS: 编辑 backendGenerator.ts<br/>5 处模板 import 字符串改写
    Dev->>FE: npx tsc --noEmit
    FE-->>Dev: 类型检查通过

    Note over Dev,CI: 阶段 3 — 测试断言 + 清理脚本 + drift 脚本
    Dev->>FS: 更新 module-governance*.spec.ts 断言<br/>pantheon-base/modules/business/*
    Dev->>FS: 修复 cleanup-generated-modules.mjs 正则<br/>pantheon-base/modules/business/
    Dev->>FS: 更新 cleanup-generated-modules.test.mjs fixture
    Dev->>FS: 调整 triage-base-drift.mjs normalizeModuleName<br/>pantheon-base/backend → MODNAME/backend
    Dev->>FE: node cleanup-generated-modules.test.mjs
    FE-->>Dev: 单测通过

    Note over Dev,CI: 阶段 4 — 边界门禁 + MFA 基线 + 覆盖率门禁
    Dev->>FS: backend/.golangci.yml 添加 depguard 规则<br/>deny modules/system 非 contracts 包
    Dev->>FS: scripts/harness/check-boundaries.mjs<br/>默认 --strict
    Dev->>FS: .github/workflows/ci.yml 追加<br/>boundary-gate + coverage-gate jobs
    Dev->>FS: docs/DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md 添加<br/>生产基线 mfa_enabled=1
    Dev->>CI: 推送 release/v0.9.0 分支
    CI->>CI: fast-checks / unit-tests / go-lint
    CI->>CI: boundary-gate (check-boundaries --strict)
    CI->>CI: coverage-gate (go test -coverprofile + 阈值)
    CI-->>Dev: 全部门禁通过 ✅

    Note over Dev,CI: 验证清单
    Dev->>FS: rg "pantheon-platform" backend/<br/>frontend/src frontend/scripts frontend/tests
    FS-->>Dev: 0 残留
    Dev->>FS: rg "pantheon-platform/backend" 全仓库
    FS-->>Dev: 仅 docs/ + .harness/evidence/ 历史记录
